    "1249": {
      "review_count": 14,
      "average_rating": 4.14,
      "html": "<div id=\"tab-reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--reviews panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div id=\"reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Reviews\"><div id=\"comments\"><h2 class=\"woocommerce-Reviews-title\">14 reviews for <span>Vyntech 7-Strap Smartwatch</span></h2><ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1001\">\n<div id=\"comment-1001\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10a?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Rohit K.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Bhai kya mast watch hai! The 7 strap combo makes it feel like I have a new watch for every day of the week. Premium build quality and display is crystal clear.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/44-ultra-7-in1-smart-watch-android-ios-zdea-yes-original-imahhfuafdembqte.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1002\">\n<div id=\"comment-1002\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10b?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Ankit Verma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Display is very smooth and bright. Straps quality is surprisingly good for the price. Battery lasts about 1.5 days with Bluetooth calling always on.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_3e4f7049d612470aadca37c21f48668f.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1003\">\n<div id=\"comment-1003\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10c?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Priya Singh</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Watch looks very premium but the app keeps disconnecting from my phone automatically in the background. I stop getting WhatsApp notifications until I open the app again.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Priya,<br><br>We apologize for the inconvenience. This happens due to strict battery optimization settings on some smartphones. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our software support expert will guide you on how to lock the app in the background for seamless notifications.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1004\">\n<div id=\"comment-1004\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10d?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Vikas D.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Here is my own review for this product: what I found. Initially I received the package but one strap was missing. Support agent on call was not very helpful. Then I used the head contact help.vyntech@gmail.com. They acknowledged my issue instantly and sent a whole new set of 7 straps within 2 days! Excellent escalation support. The watch itself is top notch.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_6eff2c1b6299480cbd6472e2bc5f48ca.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1005\">\n<div id=\"comment-1005\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10e?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sai Teja</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Chala bagundi product. The watch faces are nice and customisation is easy through the app. Only con is wireless charger wire is a bit short.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1006\">\n<div id=\"comment-1006\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10f?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 1 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:20%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">1</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Kunal R.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Screen went blank completely after 3 days of use. Not turning on even after keeping it on the wireless charger for hours. Have initiated a replacement.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Kunal,<br><br>We really apologize for the inconvenience caused by the defective unit. You need not worry, your replacement request has been approved. A brand new sealed product will be delivered to you at the time of pickup.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1007\">\n<div id=\"comment-1007\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10g?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Karthik Iyer</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Romba nalla irukku. For this price getting a premium metal body watch with 7 different quality straps is a steal deal.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_632b3d39945d4687942138808c102faa.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1008\">\n<div id=\"comment-1008\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10h?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Amit B.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Very nice received product. Calling works fine but the speaker volume feels a bit low when you are outdoors in traffic.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1009\">\n<div id=\"comment-1009\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10i?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Adarsh M.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Straps are of good quality and screen is big. But fitness tracking steps are not 100% accurate. Shows extra steps sometimes while traveling in bus.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Adarsh,<br><br>We apologize for the tracking inconsistency. Bumpy bus rides can sometimes trigger the pedometer sensors. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and we will assist you in updating the firmware, which includes better motion-calibration algorithms.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1010\">\n<div id=\"comment-1010\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10j?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Neha Patel</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Gifted this to my sister. She loved the multiple strap colors. Looks exactly like a flagship 80k watch! Nobody can tell the difference.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1011\">\n<div id=\"comment-1011\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10k?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Mohit Sharma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Good watch overall. Smooth UI and no lag while scrolling.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_359228c644f94f78a780e1a8abaea730.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1012\">\n<div id=\"comment-1012\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10l?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Rahul Singh</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Pese ki hisab se theek h. Worth the money completely with 7 straps.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1013\">\n<div id=\"comment-1013\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10m?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Arvind T.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Awesome packing and fast delivery. Touch is very responsive and calling works flawlessly.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1014\">\n<div id=\"comment-1014\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10n?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sagar M.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Everything fine - mic, fitting, build are great. Best combo watch on the internet. Highly recommended.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n</ol></div><div class=\"clear\"></div></div></div>"
    }
